Title: Dead Ringer
Plot: Grissom, Catherine and Nick investigate the death of a runner during a competition. Sara and Warrick look into the suspected murder-suicide  of a couple in a hotel room.
GuestStars: Chris Coppola, Brian D. Johnson, Neil Giuntoli, Tom Parker, Kim Rhodes, Shawn Doyle, Tina Holmes, Steven Culp, Dash Mihok, Chad Williams, Jennifer Gatti
